lead_paragraph: Striker Theo Walcott, midfielder Santi Cazorla and defenders Hector Bellerin and Nacho Monreal will miss Arsenal's Champions League Group A game at Bulgarian club Ludogorets on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Walcott, Cazorla, Bellerin, Monreal Missing for Arsenal
headline.main: Walcott, Cazorla, Bellerin, Monreal Missing for Arsenal
